show.description: In a mountainous region, a female cyclist is mysteriously murdered during a race. Months later, her sister  a journalist  goes undercover by joining the same cycling team, determined to uncover the identity of the killer. As she delves deeper, unexpected allies emerge, but who truly helped her, and what was their fate..
